00:27:10.070 --> 00:27:14.140
it.
It's a Wi-Fi enabled, and it can download

00:27:14.140 --> 00:27:18.280
music.
What I want is the model that has a Kindle-type

00:27:18.280 --> 00:27:22.540
display where the music
stand is so that I can get sheet music to

00:27:22.540 --> 00:27:24.799
appear in real time for me to
play.

00:27:24.799 --> 00:27:28.140
Why not, right?
That would make the piano more "piano-ish.",

00:27:28.140 --> 00:27:30.539
right?
That doesn't mean that I necessarily want

00:27:30.539 --> 00:27:34.350
to scan Bloomberg headlines while I'm sitting
at the keyboard but I would like to have all

00:27:34.350 --> 00:27:40.440
of my music available in the same format that
I may soon consume my books.

