00:28:34.080 --> 00:28:37.610
brand new way.
All of these devices, I think, are examples

00:28:37.610 --> 00:28:42.140
of ways in which our world
will become more intelligent with pervasive

00:28:42.140 --> 00:28:44.880
connectivity and the
opportunities that you have as Googlers to

00:28:44.880 --> 00:28:48.049
organize that information
and to deal with the new paths to consumers,

00:28:48.049 --> 00:28:53.929
and the new devices in our
lives is just tremendous.

